<i>adverb</i>: 뚝딱뚝딱 [뚝딱뚝딱] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>뚝딱뚝딱 [뚝딱뚝딱]</dt><br>
<dd>1. pounding</dd><br>
<dd>갑자기 놀라거나 겁이 나서 가슴이 자꾸 뛰는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which one's heart beats rapidly and heavily.</dd><br>
<dd>2. with a hammering sound</dd><br>
<dd>단단한 물건을 자꾸 두드리는 소리.</dd><br>
<dd>A word imitating the sound of hitting a hard object repeatedly.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>